SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2009-1
PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE 2 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT by adding the name of the Province of Manitoba and the name of 34 Indian Bands in Manitoba along with the name of the council of each Band and the description of each Band’s reserves in Manitoba, where the Band’s provincial-type tax may apply.
